Kalau kita menyorok macam tikus pun,

254
00:17:55,083 --> 00:17:56,458
mereka tetap cari kita.

255
00:17:57,125 --> 00:17:59,000
Seorang demi seorang.

256
00:17:59,708 --> 00:18:01,375
Ada satu saja jalan keluar.

257
00:18:01,708 --> 00:18:03,125
Berdepan dengan mereka.

258
00:18:04,208 --> 00:18:05,041
Dengar sini.

259
00:18:05,666 --> 00:18:06,583
Di dunia ini...

260
00:18:08,416 --> 00:18:11,208
semuanya perlu ditimbang supaya seimbang.

261
00:18:12,125 --> 00:18:13,458
Antara keuntungan

262
00:18:14,166 --> 00:18:15,166
dengan kerugian

263
00:18:15,250 --> 00:18:16,500
dan sekarang ini...

264
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:20,916
mereka rasa mereka takkan rugi apa-apa.

265
00:18:22,291 --> 00:18:24,166
Orang yang fikir begitu

266
00:18:25,833 --> 00:18:27,041
akan terlebih yakin.

267
00:18:30,250 --> 00:18:31,083
Jadi...

268
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:33,625
kitalah yang akan

269
00:18:34,458 --> 00:18:36,083
tunjukkan kepada mereka

270
00:18:38,125 --> 00:18:39,625
sebesar mana...

271
00:18:40,666 --> 00:18:41,625
kerugian mereka.

272
00:18:54,166 --> 00:18:55,125
Di mana gabenor?

273
00:18:55,708 --> 00:18:56,750
Di mana dia?

274
00:18:58,666 --> 00:18:59,541
Palermo!

275
00:19:01,375 --> 00:19:02,458
Kita ada masalah.

276
00:19:08,875 --> 00:19:09,708
Tokyo.

277
00:19:09,791 --> 00:19:11,333
Bertenang.

278
00:19:11,416 --> 00:19:13,166
- Tokyo.
- Bertenang.

279
00:19:26,416 --> 00:19:28,541
Pada kiraan tiga, tembak dan tunduk.

280
00:19:30,625 --> 00:19:31,583
Satu...

281
00:19:36,125 --> 00:19:36,958
Dua...

282
00:19:40,333 --> 00:19:41,750
Turunkan pistol, tikus!

283
00:19:44,416 --> 00:19:46,708
Biar saya perkenalkan diri.

284
00:19:47,958 --> 00:19:50,291
Saya Palermo, ketua rompakan ini.

285
00:19:50,375 --> 00:19:53,875
Acukan pistol ke sini.
Saya sasaran paling berharga.

286
00:19:53,958 --> 00:19:56,041
Jangan, acu kepada perempuan ini.

287
00:19:56,125 --> 00:19:56,958
Bagus.

288
00:19:57,541 --> 00:19:59,833
Beberapa saat lagi tembak-menembak,

289
00:19:59,916 --> 00:20:02,000
nak berbual tentang anatomi dulu?

290
00:20:04,250 --> 00:20:06,208
Manusia ada dua mata.

291
00:20:06,291 --> 00:20:07,958
Tidak seperti sumpah-sumpah,

292
00:20:08,166 --> 00:20:11,500
kedudukannya tetap
dan terletak di depan kepala.

293
00:20:14,083 --> 00:20:17,833
Kalau berlaku tembak-menembak,
susah juga awak.

294
00:20:17,916 --> 00:20:20,041
Jika awak tembak, mereka ini mati.

295
00:20:21,541 --> 00:20:23,541
Saya cakap dengan awak, Gandía.

296
00:20:24,416 --> 00:20:26,833
Mesti awak berlatih menembak setiap Ahad,

297
00:20:26,916 --> 00:20:29,041
suka baca majalah senjata api.

298
00:20:29,416 --> 00:20:32,125
Awak dah lama tunggu peluang ini,

299
00:20:32,208 --> 00:20:33,583
untuk jadi wira.

300
00:20:33,666 --> 00:20:35,375
Biar saya beri nasihat.

301
00:20:35,833 --> 00:20:37,416
Fikirlah tentang Marisa,

302
00:20:38,166 --> 00:20:41,333
bayangkan wajah Juanito,
anak awak yang comel

303
00:20:42,916 --> 00:20:45,083
dan turunkan pistol perlahan-lahan.

304
00:20:57,708 --> 00:20:58,541
Baiklah.

305
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:01,833
Baik.

306
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:32,916
Pada ketika itu, Profesor sedar

307
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:36,416
rompakan ini jauh berbeza
dengan rompakan di Kilang Wang.

308
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:39,541
Ini bukan ideanya

309
00:21:40,458 --> 00:21:43,000
dan dia tak sempat masukkan idea sendiri.

310
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:48,375
Jika dia ada butang undur,
pasti dia sudah menekannya.

311
00:21:50,250 --> 00:21:51,458
Namun, itu mustahil.

312
00:21:52,416 --> 00:21:54,000
Awak okey, Tokyo?

313
00:21:54,083 --> 00:21:55,083
Cakaplah sesuatu!

314
00:21:55,541 --> 00:21:56,375
Awak okey?

315
00:21:57,458 --> 00:21:58,833
Pergi bantu Palermo!

316
00:21:58,916 --> 00:22:02,375
Kami menembak ves mereka,
mengikut arahan Profesor.

317
00:22:02,458 --> 00:22:04,375
- Bantu Palermo!
- Kami terlewat.

318
00:22:24,250 --> 00:22:27,416
Bangun! Di mana gabenor?

319
00:22:36,333 --> 00:22:38,875
Kita perlu bawa dia keluar.
Cari pengusung!

320
00:22:48,958 --> 00:22:50,458
Sial! Semuanya jahanam!

321
00:22:50,541 --> 00:22:52,333
Matanya penuh kaca!

322
00:22:52,416 --> 00:22:53,250
Alamak!

323
00:23:00,708 --> 00:23:01,541
Tolong saya!

324
00:23:05,500 --> 00:23:06,333
Tepi!

325
00:23:06,416 --> 00:23:08,666
Rapati dinding!

326
00:23:08,750 --> 00:23:10,333
Cepat!

327
00:23:11,500 --> 00:23:13,416
Cepat! Lekas!

328
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:15,833
Cepat! Lekas! Jalan cepat!

329
00:23:15,916 --> 00:23:17,458
- Hampir tiba.
- Hati-hati.

330
00:23:19,708 --> 00:23:20,708
Jangan risau.

331
00:23:21,708 --> 00:23:23,000
Ubat tahan sakit!

332
00:23:24,666 --> 00:23:27,791
Bertenang,
saya nak tanggalkan perlahan-lahan.

333
00:23:27,875 --> 00:23:29,083
Perlahan. Hati-hati.

334
00:23:29,166 --> 00:23:30,125
Bagus.

335
00:23:35,833 --> 00:23:38,708
Okey, buka mata perlahan-lahan.

336
00:23:39,375 --> 00:23:40,291
Macam itulah.

337
00:23:43,125 --> 00:23:43,958
Bagus.

338
00:23:44,416 --> 00:23:47,416
Saya tak boleh buka terlalu lama.

339
00:23:47,500 --> 00:23:48,583
Awak nampak?

340
00:23:48,666 --> 00:23:50,750
Tak nampak apa-apa. Apa dah jadi?

341
00:23:50,833 --> 00:23:52,083
Alamak.

342
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:53,625
Okey.

343
00:23:54,375 --> 00:23:55,583
Awak nampak cahaya?

344
00:23:56,750 --> 00:23:58,541
Terang macam Stadium Maracanã.

345
00:23:59,041 --> 00:24:01,500
Apa bezanya? Awak dah jadi doktor mata?

346
00:24:01,583 --> 00:24:03,375
Dia perlukan doktor mata.

347
00:24:03,458 --> 00:24:04,875
Hubungi Profesor.

348
00:24:04,958 --> 00:24:06,000
Saya nampak kaca.

349
00:24:06,083 --> 00:24:08,375
Stockholm, peti kecemasan empat.

350
00:24:08,458 --> 00:24:09,583
- Kit bedah.
- Okey.

351
00:24:09,666 --> 00:24:10,708
Cepat.

352
00:24:14,375 --> 00:24:16,875
- Apa rancangan awak?
- Keluarkan kaca.

353
00:24:16,958 --> 00:24:18,833
- Bagaimana?
- Guna penyepit.

354
00:24:18,916 --> 00:24:20,500
Jangan memandai, Tokyo.

355
00:24:20,583 --> 00:24:23,916
Telefon Profesor,
minta tukar tiga tebusan dengan pakar.

356
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,416
- Denver! Diam, pergi!
- Okey.

357
00:24:26,500 --> 00:24:27,875
Dengar sini, Palermo.

358
00:24:27,958 --> 00:24:30,750
Tangan saya lebih stabil
daripada pakar bedah.

359
00:24:30,833 --> 00:24:32,541
Saya akan keluarkan kaca itu.

360
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:35,500
Tahu kenapa laser digunakan
untuk bedah mata?

361
00:24:35,583 --> 00:24:37,166
- Ya.
- Isu kecil saja.

362
00:24:37,250 --> 00:24:42,250
Ia sangat tepat.
Bedah mata perlukan ketepatan tinggi.

363
00:24:42,333 --> 00:24:44,125
Tengok ini, Denver.

364
00:24:44,208 --> 00:24:46,166
Tokyo nak guna penyepit

365
00:24:46,250 --> 00:24:48,500
yang dia guna untuk cabut bulunya.

366
00:24:48,583 --> 00:24:50,000
Tolonglah!

367
00:24:50,083 --> 00:24:51,000
Mengarut betul!

368
00:24:52,875 --> 00:24:53,916
Cuba sebut lagi.

369
00:24:54,583 --> 00:24:55,583
Ulanglah.

370
00:24:57,041 --> 00:24:58,500
Apa ayat saya?

371
00:24:59,666 --> 00:25:03,583
Saya yakin anu awak lembut dan licin.

372
00:25:03,666 --> 00:25:05,708
Cakap, "Saya takkan sebut

373
00:25:05,791 --> 00:25:08,375
tentang anu rakan sekerja saya lagi."

374
00:25:08,458 --> 00:25:11,333
"Saya tak sebut
tentang anu rakan sekerja lagi."

375
00:25:11,750 --> 00:25:12,583
Tak dengar.

376
00:25:13,250 --> 00:25:16,833
- Saya takkan sebut lagi, celaka.
- Bagus, Palermo.

377
00:25:18,333 --> 00:25:19,583
Kami akan bantu awak.

378
00:25:19,666 --> 00:25:21,791
Bagus, rawat mata saya nanti.

379
00:25:22,333 --> 00:25:24,250
- Denver, kanan saya.
- Nak apa?

380
00:25:24,333 --> 00:25:27,375
Pinjam tangan awak.
Awak jadi orang kanan saya.

381
00:25:27,458 --> 00:25:30,041
- Macam anjing pemandu?
- Diam!

382
00:25:30,500 --> 00:25:31,875
- Tokyo!
- Apa?

383
00:25:32,375 --> 00:25:35,875
Ada 14 tan keluli di bawah kita.
Nairobi ada dengan Bogotá?

384
00:25:35,958 --> 00:25:36,791
Betul.

385
00:25:37,583 --> 00:25:38,458
Ayuh.

386
00:25:39,625 --> 00:25:41,541
Apa rancangan kamu sebenarnya?

387
00:25:42,375 --> 00:25:44,333
Ikat kami macam anjing?

388
00:25:44,416 --> 00:25:45,291
Tak, sayang.

389
00:25:45,916 --> 00:25:49,625
Kita sekeluarga.
Jika awak nak kencing, cakap.

390
00:25:50,666 --> 00:25:51,791
Matilah awak.

391
00:25:54,083 --> 00:25:56,500
Gabenor, saya minta izin.

392
00:26:00,416 --> 00:26:02,125
Saya akan simpankan dulu.

393
00:26:03,166 --> 00:26:04,750
Minta perhatian!

394
00:26:04,833 --> 00:26:08,750
Kami pasang 460 kilogram bom

395
00:26:08,833 --> 00:26:10,625
pada semua pintu dan tingkap,

396
00:26:10,708 --> 00:26:14,500
setiap laluan keluar dan masuk,
jadi kalau sesiapa nak lari...

397
00:26:14,583 --> 00:26:15,625
Meletup!

398
00:26:16,458 --> 00:26:18,458
Mereka akan hancur berkecai.

399
00:26:19,333 --> 00:26:22,250
Tak berbaloi.

400
00:26:23,666 --> 00:26:27,875
Kita terpaksa berkurung di sini
selama beberapa hari

401
00:26:28,666 --> 00:26:30,333
tapi sepanjang tempoh itu,

402
00:26:31,625 --> 00:26:32,625
kami akan

403
00:26:33,250 --> 00:26:35,250
melindungi kamu semua.

404
00:26:35,750 --> 00:26:38,250
Sebagai balasan, kamu lindungi kami.

405
00:26:39,416 --> 00:26:40,250
Hebat.

406
00:26:41,125 --> 00:26:44,375
Bila-bila kamu mahu,
kamu boleh buka penutup mata.

407
00:26:47,125 --> 00:26:48,458
Sekarang!

408
00:26:51,208 --> 00:26:52,041
Macam mana?

409
00:26:53,250 --> 00:26:54,083
Kamu okey?

410
00:26:54,583 --> 00:26:56,958
Kita dah nampak satu sama lain,

411
00:26:57,166 --> 00:26:59,291
jadi saya perkenalkan En. Bogotá.

412
00:26:59,375 --> 00:27:01,416
Dia akan pilih empat sukarelawan.

413
00:27:03,166 --> 00:27:06,666
Nama saya Bogotá,
saya datang untuk buat kerja sukar.

414
00:27:07,625 --> 00:27:10,375
Kita akan bekerja
dalam suhu 65 darjah Celsius.

415
00:27:10,458 --> 00:27:13,041
Panas macam tempat bakar mayat.

416
00:27:13,541 --> 00:27:17,125
Kita kerja gilir-gilir
selama 12, 14, 16 atau 24 jam.

417
00:27:18,375 --> 00:27:19,625
Selagi kamu tahan.

418
00:27:20,875 --> 00:27:22,375
Siapa nak?

419
00:27:33,500 --> 00:27:34,333
Nama?

420
00:27:35,208 --> 00:27:36,041
Agustín.

421
00:27:36,958 --> 00:27:38,791
- Agustín Montero.
- Urusan apa?

422
00:27:38,875 --> 00:27:39,708
Saya datang...

423
00:27:40,666 --> 00:27:42,166
untuk tukar wang.

424
00:27:43,291 --> 00:27:44,291
Tampil ke depan.

425
00:27:44,375 --> 00:27:46,625
Tahniah, awak sukarelawan pertama.

426
00:27:47,125 --> 00:27:49,916
- Awak?
- Miguel Fernández Talanill, Murcia.

427
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:52,208
- Okey.
- Siapa awak, Miguel?

428
00:27:52,291 --> 00:27:53,875
Pelatih Bahagian Sistem.

429
00:27:56,291 --> 00:27:57,500
Unit IT.

430
00:27:58,083 --> 00:28:00,166
- Tak layak.
- Seterusnya!

431
00:28:01,583 --> 00:28:03,000
Nama, buat apa di sini?

432
00:28:03,791 --> 00:28:04,625
Alfonso.

433
00:28:04,916 --> 00:28:08,416
Urusan dengan Bahagian Hutang.

434
00:28:10,166 --> 00:28:13,666
Ke depan. Tahniah,
awak sukarelawan kedua. Seterusnya!

435
00:28:13,750 --> 00:28:15,166
Nama, buat apa di sini?

436
00:28:15,250 --> 00:28:18,000
Amanda, saya setiausaha gabenor.

437
00:28:18,375 --> 00:28:20,333
Tak layak. Seterusnya!

438
00:28:20,416 --> 00:28:21,291
Nama!

439
00:28:21,958 --> 00:28:23,125
Matías Caño.

440
00:28:23,208 --> 00:28:26,125
- Layak. Ke depan!
- Tidak, puan.

441
00:28:26,208 --> 00:28:28,875
Jangan panggil puan. Ayuh, sukarelawan.

442
00:28:29,708 --> 00:28:30,875
Bukan sukarelawan.

443
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:35,250
Tengok sini, nampak jari ini?

444
00:28:35,833 --> 00:28:38,500
Ini jari yang tunjukkan sukarelawan

445
00:28:38,583 --> 00:28:41,750
dan ia tunjuk awak berulang kali.

446
00:28:41,833 --> 00:28:44,666
Tolong ke depan,
awak dah jadi sukarelawan.

447
00:28:45,541 --> 00:28:47,791
Saya bukan sukarelawan, puan.

448
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:51,166
Ulang nama awak.

449
00:28:51,250 --> 00:28:52,125
Matías Caño.

450
00:28:52,208 --> 00:28:53,041
Apa?

451
00:28:53,125 --> 00:28:54,291
Matías Caño.

452
00:28:54,375 --> 00:28:55,750
Baiklah, Matías Caño.

453
00:28:55,833 --> 00:28:58,500
Ikut saya sekarang, celaka.

454
00:28:58,583 --> 00:29:00,875
Mari kita pergi. Cepat!

455
00:29:06,291 --> 00:29:07,125
Cepat!

456
00:29:10,208 --> 00:29:11,416
Ke arah lif!

457
00:29:13,333 --> 00:29:14,291
Jangan bergerak!

458
00:29:18,166 --> 00:29:19,000
Masuk!

459
00:29:28,250 --> 00:29:29,458
Apa halnya tadi?

460
00:29:29,541 --> 00:29:30,541
Bodoh!

461
00:29:31,041 --> 00:29:33,125
Apa maksud "bukan sukarelawan"?

462
00:29:33,208 --> 00:29:34,500
Ia lebih meyakinkan.

463
00:29:34,583 --> 00:29:37,375
Meyakinkan?
Awak fikir awak Anthony Hopkins?

464
00:29:38,875 --> 00:29:40,416
Saya jadi tebusan, bukan?

465
00:29:40,500 --> 00:29:43,625
Apa? Daripada penerbit
"Ikut saya sekarang, celaka,"

466
00:29:43,708 --> 00:29:45,666
filem lakonan tukang besi!

467
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:48,166
Lakonan saya bagus. Penipuan saya licin.

468
00:29:48,250 --> 00:29:49,958
Nak kena tampar sampai licin?

469
00:29:53,125 --> 00:29:53,958
Enam tahun!

470
00:29:54,041 --> 00:29:56,958
Enam tahun kerja dengan lelaki ini,

471
00:29:57,041 --> 00:30:00,000
dah lama saya nak hentak
kepala dia ke dinding.

472
00:30:28,833 --> 00:30:29,833
Dengar sini.

473
00:30:31,583 --> 00:30:33,250
Selama beberapa minit ini,

474
00:30:35,416 --> 00:30:36,958
nyawa kamu dalam bahaya.

475
00:30:41,583 --> 00:30:42,416
Sergio!

476
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:45,000
CNI sudah tiba.

477
00:31:17,958 --> 00:31:18,958
Intip mereka.

478
00:31:20,583 --> 00:31:21,916
Kolonel Tamayo.

479
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:22,833
Inspektor.

480
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:25,416
- Masa letupan?
- Pukul 12:04.

481
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:28,458
Kemudian, bunyi tembakan.
Banyak bom dipasang.

482
00:31:28,541 --> 00:31:30,875
- Bagaimana ia diletupkan?
- Tak pasti.

483
00:31:31,791 --> 00:31:34,208
Bom plastik. RDX. Buatan pakar.

484
00:31:34,291 --> 00:31:35,291
Itu bom palsu.

485
00:31:35,375 --> 00:31:37,166
Rasanya bukan, kolonel.

486
00:31:37,250 --> 00:31:39,541
Ada bom di muka bangunan, bumbung...

487
00:31:39,625 --> 00:31:42,416
Saya dah kaji.
Ia takkan letupkan Bank Sepanyol.

488
00:31:42,500 --> 00:31:44,625
Saya yakin mereka berkemampuan.

489
00:31:44,708 --> 00:31:47,791
Kencing pun, tiada apa-apa akan jadi.
Mereka sampah.

490
00:31:47,875 --> 00:31:49,375
- Dengar...
- Tolonglah.

491
00:31:56,708 --> 00:31:57,541
Alfonso.

492
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,291
Apa khabar?

493
00:32:00,375 --> 00:32:01,916
Habislah saya, Luis.

494
00:32:02,833 --> 00:32:03,833
Saya tak terdaya.

495
00:32:05,541 --> 00:32:07,208
Maaf. Awak perlu ambil alih.

496
00:32:08,208 --> 00:32:09,250
Jangan risau.

497
00:32:10,041 --> 00:32:11,083
Berehatlah.

498
00:32:14,125 --> 00:32:14,958
Luis.

499
00:32:17,041 --> 00:32:17,875
